{"word":"ἀκρασία","slug":"ἀκρασία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀϰρασία, ας, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀκρατής\">ἀκρατής</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prim.\">prim.</a> ‘lack of power’, hence <b><i>lack of self-control</i> <a href='B:530 7:5'>1 Cor 7:5</a>;</b> with stronger moral aspect of self-indulgence implied in<b> <a href='B:470 23:25'>Mt 23:25</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀκούω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀκρατής\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}